# Custom Domain Configuration for GitHub Pages
# 
# To use a custom domain:
# 1. Rename this file to "CNAME" (remove .example)
# 2. Replace the domain below with your actual domain
# 3. Configure DNS settings at your domain registrar
#
# Example: www.yourfamilytree.com
# 
# DNS Configuration:
# - CNAME record: www -> YOUR-USERNAME.github.io
# - A records for apex domain:
#   185.199.108.153
#   185.199.109.153
#   185.199.110.153
#   185.199.111.153
#
# Uncomment and replace with your domain:
# www.yourfamilytree.com